</header><div class="entry-content" itemprop="text"><span itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject">
<meta itemprop="url" content="https://www.novel-writing-help.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/home-pencil.jpg">
