</span>
<div class="nc_socialPanel swp_flatFresh swp_d_fullColor swp_i_fullColor swp_o_fullColor scale-100 scale-fullWidth" data-position="below" data-float="floatNone" data-count="5" data-floatColor="#f2f2f2" data-emphasize="0"><div class="nc_tweetContainer swp_fb" data-id="3" data-network="facebook"><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="https://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.novel-writing-help.com%2F" data-link="http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.novel-writing-help.com%2F" class="nc_tweet"><span class="swp_count swp_hide"><span class="iconFiller"><span class="spaceManWilly"><i class="sw sw-facebook"></i><span class="swp_share"> Share</span></span></span></span></a></div><div class="nc_tweetContainer twitter" data-id="2" data-network="twitter"><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/share?original_referer=/&text=Writing+a+Novel+Just+Got+Easier&url=https://www.novel-writing-help.com/" data-link="https://twitter.com/share?original_referer=/&text=Writing+a+Novel+Just+Got+Easier&url=https://www.novel-writing-help.com/" class="nc_tweet"><span class="swp_count swp_hide"><span class="iconFiller"><span class="spaceManWilly"><i class="sw sw-twitter"></i><span class="swp_share"> Tweet</span></span></span></span></a></div><div class="nc_tweetContainer nc_pinterest" data-id="5" data-network="pinterest"><a rel="nofollow" onClick="var e=document.createElement('script');e.setAttribute('type','text/javascript');e.setAttribute('charset','UTF-8');e.setAttribute('src','//assets.pinterest.com/js/pinmarklet.js?r='+Math.random()*99999999);document.body.appendChild(e);" class="nc_tweet noPop"><span class="swp_count swp_hide"><span class="iconFiller"><span class="spaceManWilly"><i class="sw sw-pinterest"></i><span class="swp_share"> Pin</span></span></span></span></a></div><div class="nc_tweetContainer linkedIn" data-id="4" data-network="linked_in"><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.novel-writing-help.com%2F" data-link="https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.novel-writing-help.com%2F" class="nc_tweet"><span class="swp_count swp_hide"><span class="iconFiller"><span class="spaceManWilly"><i class="sw sw-linkedin"></i><span class="swp_share"> Share</span></span></span></span></a></div><div class="nc_tweetContainer totes totesalt" data-id="6" ><span class="swp_count"><span class="swp_label">Shares</span> 238</span></div></div><div class="pf-content"><p class="intro">You know the toughest thing about novel writing? <em>Knowing where the heck to begin.</em></p>
<p>There&#8217;s no shortage of great writing advice out there. What&#8217;s harder to find is great advice on what to do first, what to do second, and so on&#8230; all the way through to the end.<br />
<span id="more-8"></span></p>
<p><img src="https://www.novel-writing-help.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/home-pencil.jpg" alt="Creative writing concept." width="300" height="358" class="alignright size-full wp-image-9" srcset="https://www.novel-writing-help.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/home-pencil.jpg 300w, https://www.novel-writing-help.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/home-pencil-251x300.jpg 251w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>
<p><strong>That&#8217;s where Novel Writing Help comes in&#8230;</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><em>It&#8217;s easy to understand.</em> I&#8217;ve assumed no prior knowledge whatsoever, and tackle every topic right from the roots.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><em>It takes a step-by-step approach.</em> Writing fiction is only difficult when you try to do everything at once. I&#8217;ve broken down the entire process into do-able chunks.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><em>And it&#8217;s free.</em> So jump right in – the water&#8217;s warm!</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p><script async src="//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js"></script><br />
<ins class="adsbygoogle"
     style="display:block; text-align:center;"
     data-ad-layout="in-article"
